v class=\"mb-8\"><h3 class=\"h3\">Contact us</h3><p class=\"pat\">Get a free consultation from us</p></div><div class=\"mb-6\"><label for=\"name\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\">Name *</label><input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary\" name=\"name\" value=\"Emmanuel Onosode\"/></div><div class=\"mb-6\"><label for=\"email\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\">Email *</label><input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary\" name=\"email\" value=\"emmanuelonosode4@gmail.com\"/></div><div class=\"mb-6\"><label for=\"service\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\">How can we help?</label><select id=\"service\" name=\"service\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary\"><option>Website Design &amp; Building</option><option>AI Automation</option><option>Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</option><option>Website Optimization (CRO)</option><option>General Inquiry</option></select></div><div class=\"mb-6\"><label for=\"message\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\">Message *</label><textarea name=\"message\" id=\"message\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary\">More Money In Jesus Name</textarea></div><div class=\"mb-4\"><label for=\"terms\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"terms\" required=\"\" class=\"mr-2\" name=\"terms\"/>I accept the terms and conditions *</label></div><div class=\"mb-4\" aria-live=\"polite\"></div><button class=\"inline-block py-3 px-6 rounded-full font-bold shadow-lg border transition-all duration-300 bg-transparent text-purple-600 border-2 border-purple-600 \">Submit</button></form><section class=\"w-full\" aria-label=\"Business Location Map\"><iframe title=\"Business Location\" 